OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry today, chance of a
OL,6,Flight shower at first. Otherwise some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells, low cloud
OL,8,Facross the east burning off this
OL,9,Fmorning. Warm or very warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will be dry with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud. Light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FApart from one or two light
OL,17,Fshowers it will be dry with a few
OL,18,Fbright or sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
